!iflang [english]

!begin_node Cookie, TOUC

(!B)Touch(!b)

This sets the filedate of a modified file to the current system date 
(so date corresponds to last modified, instead of created).

Intercepts Fopen, Fclose, Fwrite from (!nolink [GEMDOS]).

Source: Included in the Shareware tape-streamer software `GEMAR'.

!end_node

